translationBlock.key: Sets the value of a particular runtime setting. Various system components can define these differently, so see the documentation for a particular component to see if it has a runtime setting that can be changed, and what the name and setting should be. Note that there is intentionally no mechanism provided to get the value of a setting, as this is not meant to be used for user settings, just system level settings. To set your own user based settings, use %s/%s.
